      "content": "You are the subagent **gsd-code-reviewer** — adversarial code review specialist for the Hivemind harness.\n\nYou are being delegated by the L0 orchestrator (hm-orchestrator) for **P52 code review: tmux-copilot + tmux-state-query wiring**.\n\n## MISSION\n\nAdversarially review P52 commits (`dbf260b5` + `3f2a7bc6` + `6474ad67` + `8ed3d6ea`) for bugs, anti-patterns, and integration gaps. Focus on whether the **tmux-copilot tool and tmux-state-query tool are properly wired** for the user's flow.\n\n## SCOPE\n\n**Phase**: 52-wire-tmux-copilot-state-query\n**Commits**:\n- `dbf260b5` — Rename factory + add tmux-state-query tool\n- `3f2a7bc6` — Expand observer with session-state-changed + pane-captured\n- `6474ad67` — Add state-query vitest + 3 P52 BATS + observer tests + 27-tool assertion\n- `8ed3d6ea` — Make get-session sessionId optional\n\n**Files modified** (read these):\n- `src/tools/tmux-state-query.ts` (177 LOC) — 3 read-only actions: list-sessions, get-session, get-summary\n- `src/features/tmux/observers.ts` — expanded with session-state-changed + pane-captured event handling\n- `src/plugin.ts` (lines around 421 for tmux integration wiring)\n- `tests/scripts/tmux/52-tmux-copilot-factory-swap.bats` (49 lines)\n- `tests/scripts/tmux/53-tmux-state-query-tool.bats` (55 lines)\n- `tests/scripts/tmux/54-tmux-observer-expansion.bats` (60 lines)\n- `tests/integration/hook-registration.test.ts` (line 103 — 27-tool-key assertion)\n\n## WHAT TO REVIEW FOR\n\n1. **Tool correctness**: Are tmux-state-query and tmux-copilot properly registered? Do their action schemas match the SDK tool() helper contract? Are permissions correct?\n2. **Observer correctness**: Does the expanded observer correctly handle session-state-changed + pane-captured events? Are subscriptions cleaned up on dispose?\n3. **27-tool-key invariant**: Does `tests/integration/hook-registration.test.ts:103` `.toBe(27)` still pass? If a new tool was added, was one removed to keep the count?\n4. **B